_sText:
My first attempt at a Lego map.

Big thanks to Chizbone for the custom nav file, Karatekaefer for the great skybox, to BoHaRox for the custom lego textures and to MoHaX_cm for the already known palmtree prefab.

The map is a 40 player map. Started out by being a dev textured map but I felt I should go with lego textures instead.

Please use constructive criticism on what could be improved.

******************

Edit: File has been changed to correct missing textures. Thank you The Bucket for the heads up.

If you have already downloaded it please delete the old files and re-download.
